Dart to'liq obyektga yo'naltirilgan til (OOP) bo'lib, funksiyalar ham obyekt hisoblanadi. Shuningdek, async/await yordamida asinxron operatsiyalar bilan qulay ishlash mumkin.

## Funksiyalar

```dart
int qo'shish(int a, int b) => a + b;

void salom({required String ism, int yosh = 18}) {
  print('Salom $ism, yoshingiz $yosh');
}

double aylana_yuzasi(double r) => 3.14 * r * r;

String tabriklash(String ism, [String? unvon]) {
  return unvon != null ? '$unvon $ism' : ism;
}

void main() {
  print(qo'shish(3, 5));           // 8
  salom(ism: 'Malika', yosh: 23);
  salom(ism: 'Jasur');             // default yosh=18
  print(aylana_yuzasi(5));         // 78.5
  print(tabriklash('Karimov', 'Janob'));
}
```

## OOP — Sinf va Obyektlar

```dart
class Talaba {
  String ism;
  int yosh;
  double _baho;

  Talaba({required this.ism, required this.yosh, double baho = 0.0})
      : _baho = baho;

  Talaba.mehnat(String ism) : ism = ism, yosh = 18, _baho = 5.0;

  double get baho => _baho;
  set baho(double qiymat) {
    if (qiymat >= 0 && qiymat <= 5) _baho = qiymat;
  }

  void malumot() => print('$ism ($yosh yosh) — Baho: $_baho');

  @override
  String toString() => 'Talaba($ism, $yosh)';
}

class AloTalaba extends Talaba {
  String stipendiya;
  AloTalaba({required super.ism, required super.yosh, required this.stipendiya});

  @override
  void malumot() {
    super.malumot();
    print('Stipendiya: $stipendiya');
  }
}

abstract class Shakl {
  double yuzaHisoblash();
}

class Doira extends Shakl {
  double radius;
  Doira(this.radius);
  @override
  double yuzaHisoblash() => 3.14 * radius * radius;
}
```

## Async/Await va Future

```dart
Future<String> serverDanMalumot(String url) async {
  await Future.delayed(Duration(seconds: 2));
  return 'Server javobi: $url muvaffaqiyatli';
}

Stream<int> sonSanash() async* {
  for (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
    await Future.delayed(Duration(seconds: 1));
    yield i;
  }
}

void main() async {
  try {
    String natija = await serverDanMalumot('https://api.synapse.uz');
    print(natija);
  } catch (e) {
    print('Xato: $e');
  } finally {
    print('So\'rov tugadi');
  }

  await for (int son in sonSanash()) {
    print('Son: $son');
  }

  List<String> natijalar = await Future.wait([
    serverDanMalumot('url1'),
    serverDanMalumot('url2'),
  ]);
  natijalar.forEach(print);
}
```

