nazariya:
Flutter navigatsiyasi sahifalar orasida o'tishni boshqaradi. Flutter ikkita navigatsiya tizimini taklif etadi: Navigator 1.0 (imperativ) va Navigator 2.0 / go_router (deklarativ).

## Navigator 1.0 asoslari
Navigator stack (stek) asosida ishlaydi — push qo'shadi, pop olib tashlaydi.

```dart
// Sahifaga o'tish
Navigator.push(
  context,
  MaterialPageRoute(builder: (context) => TafsilotSahifa(id: 42)),
);

// Orqaga qaytish
Navigator.pop(context);

// Joriy sahifani yangi bilan almashtirish (orqaga qaytib bo'lmaydi)
Navigator.pushReplacement(
  context,
  MaterialPageRoute(builder: (context) => BoshSahifa()),
);

// Barcha sahifalarni tozalab yangi ochish
Navigator.pushAndRemoveUntil(
  context,
  MaterialPageRoute(builder: (context) => LoginSahifa()),
  (route) => false,
);
```

## Named Routes
Markazlashgan routes boshqaruvi uchun:

```dart
MaterialApp(
  initialRoute: '/',
  routes: {
    '/': (context) => BoshSahifa(),
    '/profil': (context) => ProfilSahifa(),
    '/sozlamalar': (context) => SozlamalarSahifa(),
    '/mahsulot': (context) => MahsulotSahifa(),
  },
)

// Ishlatish
Navigator.pushNamed(context, '/profil');
Navigator.pushNamed(context, '/mahsulot', arguments: {'id': 5, 'nom': 'Kitob'});

// Arguments qabul qilish
class MahsulotSahifa extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    final args = ModalRoute.of(context)!.settings.arguments as Map;
    return Scaffold(body: Text('Mahsulot: ${args['nom']}'));
  }
}
```

## Natija qaytarish
```dart
// Sahifadan natija qaytarish
final natija = await Navigator.push(
  context,
  MaterialPageRoute(builder: (context) => TanlovSahifa()),
);
if (natija != null) {
  print('Tanlandi: $natija');
}

// Sahifada natijani qaytarish
Navigator.pop(context, 'qizil rang tanlandi');
```

## go_router (zamonaviy yondashuv)
```yaml
# pubspec.yaml
dependencies:
  go_router: ^13.0.0
```

```dart
final router = GoRouter(
  initialLocation: '/',
  routes: [
    GoRoute(path: '/', builder: (context, state) => BoshSahifa()),
    GoRoute(
      path: '/mahsulot/:id',
      builder: (context, state) {
        final id = state.pathParameters['id']!;
        return MahsulotSahifa(id: int.parse(id));
      },
    ),
    GoRoute(path: '/profil', builder: (context, state) => ProfilSahifa()),
  ],
);

MaterialApp.router(routerConfig: router)

// Ishlatish
context.go('/mahsulot/42');
context.push('/profil');
context.pop();
```

## BottomNavigationBar
```dart
class AsosiyWrapper extends StatefulWidget {
  @override State<AsosiyWrapper> createState() => _AsosiyWrapperState();
}
class _AsosiyWrapperState extends State<AsosiyWrapper> {
  int _joriyIndeks = 0;
  final List<Widget> _sahifalar = [BoshSahifa(), QidiruvSahifa(), ProfilSahifa()];

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      body: IndexedStack(index: _joriyIndeks, children: _sahifalar),
      bottomNavigationBar: BottomNavigationBar(
        currentIndex: _joriyIndeks,
        onTap: (i) => setState(() => _joriyIndeks = i),
        items: [
          BottomNavigationBarItem(icon: Icon(Icons.home), label: 'Bosh'),
          BottomNavigationBarItem(icon: Icon(Icons.search), label: 'Qidirish'),
          BottomNavigationBarItem(icon: Icon(Icons.person), label: 'Profil'),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

IndexedStack sahifalar holatini saqlab qoladi — har safar qayta yuklamasdan oldingi holatini ko'rsatadi.

