nazariya:
Forma va validatsiya — foydalanuvchi ma'lumotlarini to'g'ri qabul qilishning asosi. Flutter da Form widget + GlobalKey<FormState> kombinatsiyasi kuchli va moslashuvchan yechim beradi.

## Asosiy forma tuzilmasi
```dart
class RegistratsiyaForma extends StatefulWidget {
  @override State<RegistratsiyaForma> createState() => _RegistratsiyaFormaState();
}

class _RegistratsiyaFormaState extends State<RegistratsiyaForma> {
  final _formaKaliti = GlobalKey<FormState>();
  final _ismController = TextEditingController();
  final _emailController = TextEditingController();
  final _parolController = TextEditingController();
  bool _yuborilmoqda = false;
  bool _parolKo'rsatilsin = false;

  @override
  void dispose() {
    _ismController.dispose();
    _emailController.dispose();
    _parolController.dispose();
    super.dispose();
  }

  Future<void> _yuborish() async {
    if (!_formaKaliti.currentState!.validate()) return;
    _formaKaliti.currentState!.save();

    setState(() => _yuborilmoqda = true);
    await Future.delayed(Duration(seconds: 2)); // API so'rov simulatsiyasi
    setState(() => _yuborilmoqda = false);

    ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
      SnackBar(content: Text('Muvaffaqiyatli ro\'yxatdan o\'tildi!'),
               backgroundColor: Colors.green),
    );
  }
```

## TextFormField validatsiyasi
```dart
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Form(
      key: _formaKaliti,
      child: Column(
        children: [
          TextFormField(
            controller: _ismController,
            decoration: InputDecoration(
              labelText: 'Ism',
              prefixIcon: Icon(Icons.person),
              border: OutlineInputBorder(borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12)),
            ),
            validator: (qiymat) {
              if (qiymat == null || qiymat.trim().isEmpty) return 'Ism kiritish majburiy';
              if (qiymat.trim().length < 2) return 'Ism kamida 2 harfdan iborat bo\'lsin';
              return null; // null = validatsiyadan o'tdi
            },
          ),
          SizedBox(height: 16),
          TextFormField(
            controller: _emailController,
            keyboardType: TextInputType.emailAddress,
            decoration: InputDecoration(
              labelText: 'Email',
              prefixIcon: Icon(Icons.email),
              border: OutlineInputBorder(borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12)),
            ),
            validator: (qiymat) {
              if (qiymat == null || qiymat.isEmpty) return 'Email kiritish majburiy';
              final emailRegex = RegExp(r'^[\w.-]+@[\w.-]+\.[a-z]{2,}$');
              if (!emailRegex.hasMatch(qiymat)) return 'To\'g\'ri email kiriting';
              return null;
            },
          ),
          SizedBox(height: 16),
          TextFormField(
            controller: _parolController,
            obscureText: !_parolKo'rsatilsin,
            decoration: InputDecoration(
              labelText: 'Parol',
              prefixIcon: Icon(Icons.lock),
              suffixIcon: IconButton(
                icon: Icon(_parolKo'rsatilsin ? Icons.visibility_off : Icons.visibility),
                onPressed: () => setState(() => _parolKo'rsatilsin = !_parolKo'rsatilsin),
              ),
              border: OutlineInputBorder(borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12)),
            ),
            validator: (qiymat) {
              if (qiymat == null || qiymat.isEmpty) return 'Parol kiritish majburiy';
              if (qiymat.length < 8) return 'Parol kamida 8 ta belgi bo\'lsin';
              if (!qiymat.contains(RegExp(r'[A-Z]'))) return 'Kamida 1 ta katta harf bo\'lsin';
              if (!qiymat.contains(RegExp(r'[0-9]'))) return 'Kamida 1 ta raqam bo\'lsin';
              return null;
            },
          ),
          SizedBox(height: 24),
          SizedBox(
            width: double.infinity,
            child: ElevatedButton(
              onPressed: _yuborilmoqda ? null : _yuborish,
              child: _yuborilmoqda
                ? CircularProgressIndicator(color: Colors.white)
                : Text('Ro\'yxatdan o\'tish'),
            ),
          ),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

## DropdownButtonFormField
```dart
String? _tanlangan;
DropdownButtonFormField<String>(
  value: _tanlangan,
  decoration: InputDecoration(labelText: 'Daraja', border: OutlineInputBorder()),
  items: ['Boshlang\'ich', 'O\'rta', 'Yuqori']
    .map((d) => DropdownMenuItem(value: d, child: Text(d)))
    .toList(),
  onChanged: (qiymat) => setState(() => _tanlangan = qiymat),
  validator: (q) => q == null ? 'Daraja tanlang' : null,
)
```

## FormField.onSaved
validate() va save() bo'yicha ma'lumot yig'ish:
```dart
String? _saqlangan;
TextFormField(
  onSaved: (qiymat) => _saqlangan = qiymat,
  validator: (q) => q!.isEmpty ? 'Majburiy' : null,
)
// _formaKaliti.currentState!.save() chaqirilganda onSaved ishlaydi
```

Formani reset qilish: `_formaKaliti.currentState!.reset()` — barcha maydonlarni boshlang'ich holatga qaytaradi.

