nazariya:
Riverpod — Provider paketining yangi va takomillashgan versiyasi bo'lib, uni ham Remi Roussel (Provider muallifi) yaratgan. Riverpod compile-time xatolarni aniqlash, testing qulayligi va Provider'dagi ba'zi cheklovlarni bartaraf etish uchun mo'ljallangan.

**Provider vs Riverpod farqlari:**
- Riverpod BuildContext'ga bog'liq emas
- Provider'lar global sifatida e'lon qilinadi
- Compile-time xato tekshiruvi
- Async state built-in qo'llab-quvvatlaydi
- Auto-dispose imkoniyati

**O'rnatish (flutter_riverpod):**
```yaml
dependencies:
  flutter_riverpod: ^2.4.9
  riverpod_annotation: ^2.3.3
dev_dependencies:
  riverpod_generator: ^2.3.9
  build_runner: ^2.4.7
```

**Asosiy Provider turlari:**
```dart
// 1. Provider — o'zgarmaydigan qiymat
final greetingProvider = Provider<String>((ref) => 'Salom, Dunyo!');

// 2. StateProvider — oddiy state
final counterProvider = StateProvider<int>((ref) => 0);

// 3. StateNotifierProvider — murakkab state
class CounterNotifier extends StateNotifier<int> {
  CounterNotifier() : super(0);
  void increment() => state++;
  void decrement() => state--;
}
final counterNotifierProvider = StateNotifierProvider<CounterNotifier, int>(
  (ref) => CounterNotifier(),
);

// 4. FutureProvider — async data
final userProvider = FutureProvider<User>((ref) async {
  final response = await http.get(Uri.parse('https://api.example.com/user'));
  return User.fromJson(jsonDecode(response.body));
});

// 5. StreamProvider — real-time data
final chatProvider = StreamProvider<List<Message>>((ref) {
  return FirebaseFirestore.instance.collection('messages').snapshots()
    .map((snap) => snap.docs.map((d) => Message.fromDoc(d)).toList());
});
```

**ProviderScope va ConsumerWidget:**
```dart
void main() {
  runApp(
    ProviderScope( // Ilovaning ildizida bo'lishi shart
      child: MyApp(),
    ),
  );
}

// ConsumerWidget — StatelessWidget o'rniga
class CounterPage extends ConsumerWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context, WidgetRef ref) {
    final count = ref.watch(counterProvider);
    return Scaffold(
      body: Center(child: Text('$count', style: TextStyle(fontSize: 48))),
      floatingActionButton: FloatingActionButton(
        onPressed: () => ref.read(counterProvider.notifier).state++,
        child: Icon(Icons.add),
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

**ref.watch vs ref.read vs ref.listen:**
```dart
// watch — UI qayta quriladi
final count = ref.watch(counterProvider);

// read — faqat bir marta (onPressed ichida)
ref.read(counterProvider.notifier).increment();

// listen — yon effektlar uchun (snackbar, navigation)
ref.listen<int>(counterProvider, (prev, next) {
  if (next >= 10) showDialog(...);
});
```

**AsyncValue bilan ishlash:**
```dart
final usersAsync = ref.watch(usersProvider);
return usersAsync.when(
  data: (users) => ListView.builder(...),
  loading: () => CircularProgressIndicator(),
  error: (err, stack) => Text('Xato: $err'),
);
```

**Family modifier — parametrli provider:**
```dart
final userByIdProvider = FutureProvider.family<User, int>((ref, userId) async {
  return await api.getUser(userId);
});
// Ishlatish:
ref.watch(userByIdProvider(42));
```

