Haqiqiy ilovalar tarmoq orqali serverlar bilan muloqot qiladi. Flutter'da HTTP so'rovlari uchun ikkita asosiy paket bor: `http` (sodda) va `dio` (kuchli).

**http paketi (oddiy holatlar uchun):**
```yaml
dependencies:
  http: ^1.1.0
```

```dart
import 'package:http/http.dart' as http;
import 'dart:convert';

// GET so'rov
Future<void> fetchUser(int id) async {
  final response = await http.get(
    Uri.parse('https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users/$id'),
  );
  if (response.statusCode == 200) {
    final data = jsonDecode(response.body);
    print(data['name']);
  } else {
    throw Exception('Ma\'lumot yuklanmadi: ${response.statusCode}');
  }
}

// POST so'rov
Future<void> createPost(String title, String body) async {
  final response = await http.post(
    Uri.parse('https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts'),
    headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'},
    body: jsonEncode({'title': title, 'body': body, 'userId': 1}),
  );
  print(jsonDecode(response.body));
}
```

**Dio paketi (keng imkoniyatlar):**
```yaml
dependencies:
  dio: ^5.4.0
```

```dart
import 'package:dio/dio.dart';

// Dio instansiyasini sozlash
final dio = Dio(BaseOptions(
  baseUrl: 'https://api.example.com',
  connectTimeout: Duration(seconds: 5),
  receiveTimeout: Duration(seconds: 10),
  headers: {'Authorization': 'Bearer YOUR_TOKEN'},
));

// GET
Future<List<User>> getUsers() async {
  final response = await dio.get('/users');
  return (response.data as List).map((u) => User.fromJson(u)).toList();
}

// POST
Future<void> createUser(Map<String, dynamic> userData) async {
  final response = await dio.post('/users', data: userData);
  print('Yaratildi: ${response.data}');
}

// PUT
