class Post {
  final int id;
  final String title;
  final User author; // Nested ob'ekt
  final List<Comment> comments; // Nested ro'yxat

  Post({required this.id, required this.title, 
        required this.author, required this.comments});

  factory Post.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) => _$PostFromJson(json);
  Map<String, dynamic> toJson() => _$PostToJson(this);
}
```

**Enum bilan:**
```dart
