Cloud Firestore — Firebase'ning NoSQL bulut ma'lumotlar bazasi. Real-time sync, offline support va kuchli so'rov imkoniyatlari bilan mobil ilovalar uchun ideal.

**O'rnatish:**
```yaml
dependencies:
  cloud_firestore: ^4.14.0
```

**Firestore tuzilmasi:**
- `Collection` — jadvalga o'xshaydi (users, posts, products)
- `Document` — bitta yozuv (har bir foydalanuvchi)
- `Subcollection` — document ichidagi collection

**CRUD operatsiyalari:**
```dart
final db = FirebaseFirestore.instance;

// CREATE — yangi document (auto ID)
Future<void> addUser(String name, String email) async {
  await db.collection('users').add({
    'name': name,
    'email': email,
    'createdAt': FieldValue.serverTimestamp(),
    'isActive': true,
  });
}

// CREATE — o'z ID bilan
Future<void> setUser(String uid, Map<String, dynamic> data) async {
  await db.collection('users').doc(uid).set(data);
  // yoki merge: true bilan (mavjud ma'lumotni o'chirmaydi)
  await db.collection('users').doc(uid).set(data, SetOptions(merge: true));
}

// READ — bitta document
Future<Map<String, dynamic>?> getUser(String uid) async {
  final doc = await db.collection('users').doc(uid).get();
  if (doc.exists) return doc.data();
  return null;
}

// READ — barcha documentlar
Future<List<Map<String, dynamic>>> getAllUsers() async {
  final snapshot = await db.collection('users').get();
  return snapshot.docs.map((doc) => {'id': doc.id, ...doc.data()}).toList();
}

// UPDATE — faqat ko'rsatilgan maydonlarni yangilash
Future<void> updateUser(String uid, String newName) async {
  await db.collection('users').doc(uid).update({
    'name': newName,
    'updatedAt': FieldValue.serverTimestamp(),
  });
}

// DELETE
Future<void> deleteUser(String uid) async {
  await db.collection('users').doc(uid).delete();
}
```

**Real-time Stream:**
```dart
// Bitta document'ni kuzatish
Stream<DocumentSnapshot> watchUser(String uid) {
  return db.collection('users').doc(uid).snapshots();
}

// Collection'ni kuzatish
Stream<List<Map<String, dynamic>>> watchUsers() {
  return db.collection('users')
    .orderBy('name')
    .snapshots()
    .map((snap) => snap.docs
      .map((doc) => {'id': doc.id, ...doc.data()})
      .toList());
}

// UI da:
StreamBuilder<QuerySnapshot>(
  stream: db.collection('users').snapshots(),
  builder: (ctx, snap) {
    if (!snap.hasData) return CircularProgressIndicator();
    return ListView.builder(
      itemCount: snap.data!.docs.length,
      itemBuilder: (ctx, i) {
        final user = snap.data!.docs[i];
        return ListTile(title: Text(user['name']));
      },
    );
  },
)
```

