Firebase Storage rasm, video, PDF kabi fayllarni bulutda saqlaydi. Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) esa push bildirishnomalar yuborish uchun ishlatiladi.

**Firebase Storage o'rnatish:**
```yaml
dependencies:
  firebase_storage: ^11.5.6
  image_picker: ^1.0.7  # Rasm tanlash uchun
```

**Fayl yuklash:**
```dart
class StorageService {
  final _storage = FirebaseStorage.instance;
  final _auth = FirebaseAuth.instance;

  // Profil rasmi yuklash
  Future<String> uploadProfilePhoto(XFile imageFile) async {
    final uid = _auth.currentUser!.uid;
    final ext = imageFile.path.split('.').last;
    final ref = _storage.ref('users/$uid/profile.$ext');

    // Fayl yuklash
    final uploadTask = ref.putFile(
      File(imageFile.path),
      SettableMetadata(contentType: 'image/$ext'),
    );

    // Progress kuzatish
    uploadTask.snapshotEvents.listen((event) {
      final progress = event.bytesTransferred / event.totalBytes;
      print('${(progress * 100).toStringAsFixed(1)}% yuklandi');
    });

    // Yuklash tugashini kutish
    await uploadTask;

    // Download URL olish
    return await ref.getDownloadURL();
  }

  // Umumiy fayl yuklash
  Future<String> uploadFile(String localPath, String storagePath) async {
    final ref = _storage.ref(storagePath);
    await ref.putFile(File(localPath));
    return await ref.getDownloadURL();
  }

  // Fayl o'chirish
  Future<void> deleteFile(String storagePath) async {
    await _storage.ref(storagePath).delete();
  }

  // URL dan fayl o'chirish
  Future<void> deleteByUrl(String downloadUrl) async {
    final ref = _storage.refFromURL(downloadUrl);
    await ref.delete();
  }
}
```

**Rasm tanlash va yuklash (UI bilan):**
```dart
