nazariya:
Flutter animatsiyalar tizimi juda kuchli va moslashuvchan. Animatsiyalar foydalanuvchi tajribasini yaxshilaydi va UI ni jonlantiradi.

## AnimationController

AnimationController animatsiyaning vaqt oralig'ini va yo'nalishini boshqaradi:

```dart
class _MyWidgetState extends State<MyWidget> with SingleTickerProviderStateMixin {
  late AnimationController _controller;

  @override
  void initState() {
    super.initState();
    _controller = AnimationController(
      duration: const Duration(milliseconds: 500),
      vsync: this,
    );
  }

  @override
  void dispose() {
    _controller.dispose(); // muhim!
    super.dispose();
  }
}
```

`vsync: this` — ekran yangilanishi bilan sinxronlash uchun. `SingleTickerProviderStateMixin` yoki `TickerProviderStateMixin` (bir nechta) ishlatiladi.

## Tween

Tween boshlang'ich va oxirgi qiymatlarni interpolatsiya qiladi:

```dart
Animation<double> _animation = Tween<double>(
  begin: 0.0,
  end: 1.0,
).animate(_controller);

// Curve bilan:
Animation<double> _curvedAnimation = Tween<double>(
  begin: 0.0,
  end: 300.0,
).animate(CurvedAnimation(
  parent: _controller,
