Dart bitta thread da ishlaydi (event loop). Og'ir hisob-kitob UI ni bloklashi mumkin — buning oldini olish uchun Isolate ishlatiladi.

## Muammo

```dart
// BU UI ni bloklaydi!
int heavyCalc(int n) {
  int result = 0;
  for (int i = 0; i < n * 1000000; i++) result += i;
  return result;
}

// Bu xato — UI jaymaydi
ElevatedButton(
  onPressed: () {
    final result = heavyCalc(1000); // UI muzlaydi
    setState(() => _result = result);
  },
)
```

## compute() — oson yechim

```dart
import 'package:flutter/foundation.dart';

Future<void> _runHeavyTask() async {
  // compute avtomatik yangi isolate yaratadi
  final result = await compute(heavyCalc, 1000);
  setState(() => _result = result);
}

// Top-level yoki static funksiya bo'lishi SHART
int heavyCalc(int n) {
  int result = 0;
  for (int i = 0; i < n * 1000000; i++) result += i;
  return result;
}
```

## To'liq Isolate.spawn()

```dart
import 'dart:isolate';

Future<void> _runIsolate() async {
  final receivePort = ReceivePort();

  await Isolate.spawn(
    _isolateFunction,
    receivePort.sendPort,
  );

  final result = await receivePort.first;
  print('Natija: $result');
}

// Top-level funksiya (isolate ichida closure ishlamaydi!)
void _isolateFunction(SendPort sendPort) {
  int result = 0;
  for (int i = 0; i < 1000000000; i++) result += i;
  sendPort.send(result);
}
```

## Ikki tomonlama muloqot

```dart
void _bidirectionalIsolate() async {
  final mainReceive = ReceivePort();

  await Isolate.spawn(_worker, mainReceive.sendPort);

  final isolateSendPort = await mainReceive.first as SendPort;

  final responsePort = ReceivePort();
  isolateSendPort.send([42, responsePort.sendPort]);
  final result = await responsePort.first;
  print(result);
}

void _worker(SendPort mainSend) {
  final workerReceive = ReceivePort();
  mainSend.send(workerReceive.sendPort);

  workerReceive.listen((message) {
    final List data = message;
    final int input = data[0];
    final SendPort reply = data[1];
    reply.send(input * input);
  });
}
```

## Isolate.run() (Dart 2.19+)

```dart
// Eng zamonaviy va sodda yol
final result = await Isolate.run(() {
  return expensiveJsonParse(largeData);
});
```

## JSON parse uchun amaliy misol

```dart
Future<List<Product>> parseProductsInBackground(String jsonStr) async {
  return await compute(_parseProducts, jsonStr);
}

List<Product> _parseProducts(String jsonStr) {
  final List data = json.decode(jsonStr);
  return data.map((e) => Product.fromJson(e)).toList();
}
```

Isolate xotirani ulashmaydi — faqat message passing orqali muloqot qiladi. compute() yengil wrapper bo'lib, ko'p holatlar uchun yetarli. Juda ko'p isolate yaratish ham resurs talab qiladi.

