nazariya:
In-app purchases (IAP) ilovadan bevosita to'lov qilish imkonini beradi. Flutter da `in_app_purchase` paketi rasmiy tavsiya etiladi.

## O'rnatish

```yaml
dependencies:
  in_app_purchase: ^3.1.0
```

## Asosiy tushunchalar

- **Consumable** — bir marta ishlatiladigan (sikkalar, hayot)
- **Non-consumable** — abadiy (premium unlock, reklama o'chirish)
- **Subscription** — obuna (oylik, yillik)

## Mahsulotlarni yuklash

```dart
import 'package:in_app_purchase/in_app_purchase.dart';

class PurchaseService {
  final InAppPurchase _iap = InAppPurchase.instance;

  static const _productIds = {'premium_unlock', 'coin_pack_100'};

  Future<List<ProductDetails>> loadProducts() async {
    final available = await _iap.isAvailable();
    if (!available) return [];

    final response = await _iap.queryProductDetails(_productIds);
    if (response.error != null) {
      print('Xato: ${response.error}');
      return [];
    }
    return response.productDetails;
  }
}
```

## Xarid qilish

```dart
Future<void> buyProduct(ProductDetails product) async {
  final purchaseParam = PurchaseParam(productDetails: product);

  if (product.id == 'coin_pack_100') {
    // Consumable
    await _iap.buyConsumable(purchaseParam: purchaseParam);
  } else {
    // Non-consumable yoki Subscription
    await _iap.buyNonConsumable(purchaseParam: purchaseParam);
  }
}
```

## Stream bilan kuzatish

```dart
late StreamSubscription<List<PurchaseDetails>> _subscription;

void initPurchases() {
  _subscription = _iap.purchaseStream.listen(
    _handlePurchases,
    onError: (e) => print('Xato: $e'),
  );
}

void _handlePurchases(List<PurchaseDetails> purchases) {
  for (final purchase in purchases) {
    switch (purchase.status) {
      case PurchaseStatus.purchased:
        _verifyAndDeliver(purchase);
        break;
      case PurchaseStatus.restored:
        _deliverProduct(purchase);
        break;
      case PurchaseStatus.error:
        print('Xarid xatosi: ${purchase.error}');
        break;
      default:
        break;
    }

    if (purchase.pendingCompletePurchase) {
      _iap.completePurchase(purchase); // muhim!
    }
  }
}
```

## Server-side tasdiqlash

```dart
Future<void> _verifyAndDeliver(PurchaseDetails purchase) async {
  // MUHIM: receipt ni serverda tekshiring
  final verified = await _verifyWithServer(
    purchase.verificationData.serverVerificationData
  );

  if (verified) {
    _deliverProduct(purchase);
  }
}
```

## Restore purchases

```dart
ElevatedButton(
  onPressed: () => InAppPurchase.instance.restorePurchases(),
  child: const Text('Xaridlarni tiklash'),
)
```

Amaliyotda: Google Play Console da mahsulotlar yaratish, App Store Connect sozlamasi, va server-side validation kerak. Test uchun sandbox/test account ishlatiladi.

