nazariya:
Flutter ilovalarida performance (ishlash tezligi) optimizatsiyasi professional dasturchilar uchun muhim ko'nikmalardan biridir. Yomon optimizallashtirilgan ilova foydalanuvchini yo'qotadi — chunki 60 FPS (frame per second) dan past ishlash ekranda «jank» (titroq, sekinlik) sifatida ko'rinadi.

## Flutter Rendering Pipeline
Flutter har bir freymni 3 bosqichda render qiladi:
1. **Build** — widget daraxti quriladi
2. **Layout** — o'lchamlar hisoblanadi
3. **Paint** — piksellarga chiziladi

Bu jarayon 16ms ichida tugashi kerak (60 FPS uchun). Agar uzoqroq ketsa — «jank» paydo bo'ladi.

## DevTools bilan Profiling
Flutter DevTools — rasmiy performance vositasi.

```bash
# Terminal orqali ishga tushirish
flutter run --profile
flutter pub global activate devtools
flutter pub global run devtools
```

**Performance Overlay** yoqish:
```dart
MaterialApp(
  showPerformanceOverlay: true, // ikki chiziq: GPU va CPU
  home: MyHomePage(),
);
```

## const Constructor
Eng oddiy optimizatsiya — `const` ishlatish:
```dart
// Yomon:
Widget build(BuildContext context) {
  return Container(
    child: Text('Salom'), // har build da yangi Text yaratiladi
  );
}

// Yaxshi:
Widget build(BuildContext context) {
  return const Text('Salom'); // qayta ishlatiladi
}
```

## RepaintBoundary
Katta widget daraxtlarida faqat o'zgargan qismni qayta chizish uchun:
```dart
RepaintBoundary(
  child: AnimatedWidget(), // faqat bu qism qayta chiziladi
)
```

## ListView optimizatsiyasi
```dart
// Yomon — hammasi bir vaqtda yuklanadi:
ListView(
  children: items.map((e) => ItemCard(e)).toList(),
)

// Yaxshi — lazy loading:
ListView.builder(
  itemCount: items.length,
  itemBuilder: (ctx, i) => ItemCard(items[i]),
)

// Eng yaxshi — katta ro'yxatlar uchun:
ListView.separated(
  itemCount: items.length,
  separatorBuilder: (_, __) => const Divider(),
  itemBuilder: (ctx, i) => ItemCard(items[i]),
)
```

## Isolate — og'ir hisoblashlar uchun
```dart
import 'dart:isolate';

// UI thread ni bloklash o'rniga alohida isolate da ishlat
Future<int> heavyCalculation(int n) async {
  return await compute(_fibonacci, n);
}

int _fibonacci(int n) {
  if (n <= 1) return n;
  return _fibonacci(n - 1) + _fibonacci(n - 2);
}

// Widget ichida:
ElevatedButton(
  onPressed: () async {
    final result = await heavyCalculation(40);
    setState(() => _result = result);
  },
  child: const Text('Hisobla'),
)
```

## Image Optimizatsiyasi
```dart
// cacheWidth/cacheHeight bilan xotira tejaymiz
Image.network(
  url,
  cacheWidth: 300,
  cacheHeight: 300,
  filterQuality: FilterQuality.low,
)

// cached_network_image paketi:
CachedNetworkImage(
  imageUrl: url,
  placeholder: (_, __) => const CircularProgressIndicator(),
  errorWidget: (_, __, ___) => const Icon(Icons.error),
)
```

## shouldRebuild — CustomPainter optimizatsiyasi
```dart
class MyPainter extends CustomPainter {
  final Color color;
  MyPainter(this.color);

  @override
  void paint(Canvas canvas, Size size) {
    canvas.drawCircle(Offset(100, 100), 50, Paint()..color = color);
  }

  @override
  bool shouldRepaint(MyPainter old) => old.color != color; // faqat kerak bo'lsa
}
```

## Xulosa
Flutter profiling — bu ilova sezgirligini o'lchash va yaxshilash jarayoni. `const` ishlatish, `ListView.builder`, `RepaintBoundary`, `compute()` va `CachedNetworkImage` — asosiy qurollar.

