## Nima uchun muhim?
- Dunyo aholisining ~15% qandaydir nogizonlik bilan yashaydi
- Ko'plab mamlakatlarda accessibility qonun talabi (ADA, WCAG 2.1)
- Screen reader foydalanuvchilari (TalkBack — Android, VoiceOver — iOS)

## Semantics Widget
```dart
Semantics(
  label: 'Profil rasmi, Mukhammad Khalikov',
  hint: 'Profilni ochish uchun bosing',
  button: true,
  child: GestureDetector(
    onTap: () => Navigator.pushNamed(context, '/profile'),
    child: CircleAvatar(backgroundImage: NetworkImage(userImageUrl)),
  ),
)
```

## Asosiy parametrlar
```dart
Semantics(
  // Screen reader uchun matn
  label: 'Yopish tugmasi',

  // Qo'shimcha yo'riqnoma
  hint: 'Dialog oynani yopadi',

  // Holat ma'lumoti
  value: 'Tanlangan: Uzbek',

  // Widget turi
  button: false,
  image: false,
  header: true,
  checked: false,
  selected: true,
  enabled: true,

  // Amallar
  onTap: () {},
  onLongPress: () {},

  child: const Text('Uzbek'),
)
```

## MergeSemantics
Bir nechta bolalarni birlashtirib bitta screen reader o'qishi uchun:
```dart
MergeSemantics(
  child: Row(
    children: [
      const Icon(Icons.star),
      const Text('4.8'),
      const Text(' (120 ta sharh)'),
    ],
  ),
  // Screen reader: "Yulduz, 4.8, 120 ta sharh" deb o'qiydi
)
```

## ExcludeSemantics
Dekorativ elementlarni screen reader dan yashirish:
```dart
ExcludeSemantics(
  child: Icon(Icons.decorative_background), // screen reader o'tmaydi
)
```

