nazariya:
Internationalization (i18n) — ilovani bir nechta tillarda ishlatish imkonini beradi. Flutter rasmiy `flutter_localizations` va `intl` paketlari orqali bu jarayonni avtomatlashtirib beradi. ARB (Application Resource Bundle) — tarjima fayllarining standarti.

## O'rnatish
`pubspec.yaml`:
```yaml
dependencies:
  flutter:
    sdk: flutter
  flutter_localizations:
    sdk: flutter
  intl: ^0.18.0

flutter:
  generate: true
```

`l10n.yaml` (loyiha ildizida):
```yaml
arb-dir: lib/l10n
template-arb-file: app_en.arb
output-localization-file: app_localizations.dart
```

## ARB fayl yaratish
`lib/l10n/app_en.arb`:
```json
{
  "@@locale": "en",
  "appTitle": "SYNAPSE",
  "@appTitle": {
    "description": "Ilova nomi"
  },
  "welcomeMessage": "Welcome, {name}!",
  "@welcomeMessage": {
    "description": "Foydalanuvchini kutib olish",
    "placeholders": {
      "name": {
        "type": "String",
        "example": "Mukhammad"
      }
    }
  },
  "lessonCount": "{count, plural, =0{No lessons} =1{1 lesson} other{{count} lessons}}",
  "@lessonCount": {
    "description": "Dars soni",
    "placeholders": {
      "count": {"type": "int"}
    }
  }
}
```

`lib/l10n/app_uz.arb`:
```json
{
  "@@locale": "uz",
  "appTitle": "SYNAPSE",
  "welcomeMessage": "Xush kelibsiz, {name}!",
  "lessonCount": "{count, plural, =0{Dars yo'q} =1{1 ta dars} other{{count} ta dars}}"
}
```

`lib/l10n/app_ru.arb`:
```json
{
  "@@locale": "ru",
  "appTitle": "SYNAPSE",
  "welcomeMessage": "Добро пожаловать, {name}!",
  "lessonCount": "{count, plural, =0{Нет уроков} =1{1 урок} other{{count} уроков}}"
}
```

## Kod generatsiyasi
```bash
flutter gen-l10n
# yoki avto-generatsiya:
flutter pub get
```

## MaterialApp sozlash
```dart
import 'package:flutter_localizations/flutter_localizations.dart';
import 'package:flutter_gen/gen_l10n/app_localizations.dart';

class MyApp extends StatefulWidget {
  const MyApp({super.key});
  @override
  State<MyApp> createState() => _MyAppState();
}

class _MyAppState extends State<MyApp> {
  Locale _locale = const Locale('uz');

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return MaterialApp(
      locale: _locale,
      supportedLocales: const [
        Locale('uz'),
        Locale('ru'),
        Locale('en'),
      ],
      localizationsDelegates: const [
        AppLocalizations.delegate,
        GlobalMaterialLocalizations.delegate,
        GlobalWidgetsLocalizations.delegate,
        GlobalCupertinoLocalizations.delegate,
      ],
      home: HomePage(
        onLocaleChange: (l) => setState(() => _locale = l),
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

## Tarjimalarni ishlatish
```dart
