nazariya:
Flutter 2.10 dan boshlab Windows, 2.13 dan macOS va Linux uchun stable desktop support mavjud. Bitta Flutter kod bazasidan 6 ta platformaga (iOS, Android, Web, Windows, macOS, Linux) chiqish mumkin.

## Sozlash
```bash
# Desktop support yoqish:
flutter config --enable-windows-desktop
flutter config --enable-macos-desktop
flutter config --enable-linux-desktop

# Mavjud loyihaga qo'shish:
flutter create --platforms windows,macos,linux .

# Run:
flutter run -d windows
flutter run -d macos
flutter run -d linux

# Build:
flutter build windows --release  # build/windows/x64/runner/Release/
flutter build macos --release    # build/macos/Build/Products/Release/
flutter build linux --release    # build/linux/x64/release/bundle/
```

## Window o'lchami va sarlavha
```dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:window_manager/window_manager.dart'; // pub.dev

void main() async {
  WidgetsFlutterBinding.ensureInitialized();
  await windowManager.ensureInitialized();

  WindowOptions windowOptions = const WindowOptions(
    size: Size(1280, 720),
    minimumSize: Size(800, 600),
    center: true,
    title: 'SYNAPSE Desktop',
    backgroundColor: Colors.transparent,
    skipTaskbar: false,
    titleBarStyle: TitleBarStyle.normal,
  );

  windowManager.waitUntilReadyToShow(windowOptions, () async {
    await windowManager.show();
    await windowManager.focus();
  });

  runApp(const MyApp());
}
```

