GraphQL — REST APIga muqobil bo'lgan so'rov tili bo'lib, mijoz aniq qaysi ma'lumotlarni olishini o'zi belgilaydi. Flutter loyihalarida GraphQL bilan ishlash uchun asosan ikkita kutubxona qo'llaniladi: **Ferry** va **Artemis**.

**Ferry** — Flutter uchun to'liq tipli GraphQL client. U reaktiv (stream-based) arxitekturada ishlaydi va `gql`, `ferry`, `ferry_flutter` paketlaridan iborat.

**Artemis** esa GraphQL schema asosida Dart kodi generatsiya qiladi. Siz `.graphql` fayllarga so'rovlarni yozasiz, Artemis ularni type-safe Dart classlariga aylantiradi.

**O'rnatish (pubspec.yaml):**
```yaml
dependencies:
  ferry: ^0.15.0
  ferry_flutter: ^0.8.0
  gql_http_link: ^0.4.0
  hive: ^2.2.3

dev_dependencies:
  ferry_generator: ^0.10.0
  build_runner: ^2.4.0
```

**Client sozlash:**
```dart
import 'package:ferry/ferry.dart';
import 'package:gql_http_link/gql_http_link.dart';

final link = HttpLink('https://api.example.com/graphql');
final client = Client(link: link);
```

**GraphQL so'rovi (.graphql fayl):**
```graphql
query GetUsers {
  users {
    id
    name
    email
  }
}
```

**Kod generatsiya:**
```bash
dart run build_runner build
```
Bu buyruq `get_users.req.dart`, `get_users.data.dart`, `get_users.var.dart` fayllarini yaratadi.

**Flutter UI bilan ishlatish:**
```dart
Operation(
  client: client,
  operationRequest: GGetUsersReq(),
  builder: (context, response, error) {
    if (response?.loading == true) {
      return CircularProgressIndicator();
    }
    final users = response?.data?.users ?? [];
    return ListView.builder(
      itemCount: users.length,
      itemBuilder: (ctx, i) => ListTile(
        title: Text(users[i].name),
        subtitle: Text(users[i].email),
      ),
    );
  },
);
```

**Mutation misoli:**
```graphql
mutation CreateUser($name: String!, $email: String!) {
  createUser(name: $name, email: $email) {
    id
    name
  }
}
```
```dart
final req = GCreateUserReq(
  (b) => b
    ..vars.name = 'Ali'
    ..vars.email = 'ali@example.com',
);
await client.request(req).first;
```

**Cache boshqaruvi:** Ferry Hive orqali offline cache qo'llab-quvvatlaydi. `TypedInMemoryStore` yoki `HiveStore` ishlatiladi. GraphQL Flutter dasturlashda kuchli type-safety va avtomatik kod generatsiyasi tufayli katta jamoalar uchun juda qulay.

