WebSocket — ikki tomonlama, doimiy TCP ulanishni ta'minlovchi protokol. HTTP'dan farqli o'laroq, WebSocket serverdan mijozga ham, mijozdan serverga ham istalgan vaqt ma'lumot yuborishi mumkin. Bu real-time chat, live dashboard, multiplayer o'yin, va jonli kurs o'zgarishlari kabi ilovalarda zarur.

**Flutter'da WebSocket ishlash usullari:**
1. Dart SDK ichida kelgan `dart:io` `WebSocket` klassi
2. `web_socket_channel` paketi (tavsiya etiladi)

**O'rnatish:**
```yaml
dependencies:
  web_socket_channel: ^2.4.0
```

**Ulanish va xabar qabul qilish:**
```dart
import 'package:web_socket_channel/web_socket_channel.dart';

final channel = WebSocketChannel.connect(
  Uri.parse('wss://echo.websocket.org'),
);

// Xabar yuborish
channel.sink.add('Salom, WebSocket!');

// Xabar qabul qilish
channel.stream.listen((message) {
  print('Keldi: $message');
});

// Ulanishni yopish
channel.sink.close();
```

**StreamBuilder bilan UI:**
```dart
StreamBuilder(
  stream: channel.stream,
  builder: (context, snapshot) {
    if (snapshot.hasData) {
      return Text('Oxirgi xabar: ${snapshot.data}');
    }
    return Text('Kutilmoqda...');
  },
)
```

**Real-time chat namunasi:**
```dart
class ChatScreen extends StatefulWidget { ... }

class _ChatScreenState extends State<ChatScreen> {
  late WebSocketChannel channel;
  final messages = <String>[];
  final controller = TextEditingController();

  @override
  void initState() {
    super.initState();
    channel = WebSocketChannel.connect(
      Uri.parse('wss://your-chat-server.com/ws'),
    );
    channel.stream.listen((msg) {
      setState(() => messages.add(msg));
    });
  }

  void sendMessage() {
    channel.sink.add(controller.text);
    controller.clear();
  }

  @override
  void dispose() {
    channel.sink.close();
    super.dispose();
  }

  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold(
      body: Column(
        children: [
          Expanded(
            child: ListView.builder(
              itemCount: messages.length,
              itemBuilder: (ctx, i) => ListTile(title: Text(messages[i])),
            ),
          ),
          Row(
            children: [
              Expanded(child: TextField(controller: controller)),
              IconButton(onPressed: sendMessage, icon: Icon(Icons.send)),
            ],
          ),
        ],
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

**JSON xabar formati:**
```dart
import 'dart:convert';

// Yuborish
channel.sink.add(jsonEncode({
  'type': 'message',
  'text': 'Salom!',
  'userId': '123',
}));

// Qabul qilish
channel.stream.listen((raw) {
  final data = jsonDecode(raw);
  print(data['text']);
});
```

**Reconnect logikasi:** Internet uzilganda avtomatik qayta ulanish uchun `dart:async` Timer ishlatiladi. `onDone` callback'da qayta ulanishni boshlaymiz. Production loyihalarda eksponensial backoff algoritmini qo'llash tavsiya etiladi.

