Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) — past energiya sarflovchi, qisqa masofali simsiz aloqa protokoli. IoT qurilmalar, smart soatlar, fitness trackerlar, va sog'liqni saqlash qurilmalari bilan muloqot qilish uchun ishlatiladi. Flutter'da BLE bilan ishlash uchun `flutter_blue_plus` paketi qo'llaniladi (`flutter_blue` eskirgan).

**O'rnatish:**
```yaml
dependencies:
  flutter_blue_plus: ^1.31.0
```

**Android ruxsatlar (AndroidManifest.xml):**
```xml
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.BLUETOOTH_SCAN" />
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.BLUETOOTH_CONNECT" />
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION" />
```

**iOS ruxsatlar (Info.plist):**
```xml
<key>NSBluetoothAlwaysUsageDescription</key>
<string>BLE qurilmalar bilan ishlash uchun</string>
```

**Bluetooth holatini tekshirish:**
```dart
import 'package:flutter_blue_plus/flutter_blue_plus.dart';

// Bluetooth yoqilganmi?
FlutterBluePlus.adapterState.listen((state) {
  if (state == BluetoothAdapterState.on) {
    print('Bluetooth yoqilgan');
  }
});
```

**Qurilmalarni scan qilish:**
```dart
await FlutterBluePlus.startScan(timeout: Duration(seconds: 4));

FlutterBluePlus.scanResults.listen((results) {
  for (ScanResult r in results) {
    print('Topildi: ${r.device.platformName} — RSSI: ${r.rssi}');
  }
});

await FlutterBluePlus.stopScan();
```

**Qurilmaga ulanish:**
```dart
BluetoothDevice device = scanResult.device;

await device.connect(timeout: Duration(seconds: 10));
print('Ulandi: ${device.platformName}');

// Ulanishni yopish
await device.disconnect();
```

**Servislar va Characteristic'lar:**
```dart
// Servislarni olish
List<BluetoothService> services = await device.discoverServices();

for (BluetoothService service in services) {
  print('Servis UUID: ${service.uuid}');

  for (BluetoothCharacteristic c in service.characteristics) {
    print('Char UUID: ${c.uuid}');

    // Ma'lumot o'qish
    if (c.properties.read) {
      List<int> value = await c.read();
      print('Qiymat: $value');
    }

    // Ma'lumot yozish
    if (c.properties.write) {
      await c.write([0x01, 0x02]);
    }

    // Notify (o'zgarishlarni kuzatish)
    if (c.properties.notify) {
      await c.setNotifyValue(true);
      c.onValueReceived.listen((value) {
        print('Yangi qiymat: $value');
      });
    }
  }
}
```

**Ulanish holati kuzatish:**
```dart
device.connectionState.listen((state) {
  if (state == BluetoothConnectionState.connected) {
    print('Ulandi');
  } else {
    print('Uzildi');
  }
});
```

**Muhim eslatmalar:** BLE bilan ishlashda `permission_handler` paketi yordamida runtime ruxsatlarni so'rash zarur. Android 12+ da `BLUETOOTH_SCAN` va `BLUETOOTH_CONNECT` ruxsatlari alohida so'raladi. Emulator'da BLE ishlamaydi — haqiqiy qurilma kerak.

