Clean Architecture — Robert C. Martin (Uncle Bob) tomonidan taklif etilgan arxitektura yondashuvi bo'lib, kodni qatlamlarga (layers) ajratish va har bir qatlam o'z mas'uliyatiga ega bo'lishiga asoslanadi.

## Nima uchun Clean Architecture?

Oddiy Flutter loyihasida vaqt o'tishi bilan quyidagi muammolar yuzaga keladi:
- Widget ichida to'g'ridan-to'g'ri API chaqiruvlar
- Business logic va UI aralashib ketadi
- Test yozish deyarli imkonsiz
- Yangi xususiyat qo'shganda boshqa joylar buziladi

Clean Architecture bu muammolarni hal qiladi.

## 3 ta asosiy qatlam

```
┌─────────────────────────────┐
│   PRESENTATION LAYER        │  ← Widgets, BLoC/Cubit, UI
├─────────────────────────────┤
│   DOMAIN LAYER              │  ← Entities, Use Cases, Repo interfaces
├─────────────────────────────┤
│   DATA LAYER                │  ← Models, Repositories impl, DataSources
└─────────────────────────────┘

Qoida: Ichki qatlam tashqi qatlam haqida HECH NARSA bilmaydi!
```

## Domain Layer — eng muhim qatlam

```dart
// domain/entities/user.dart
// Entity — toza Dart klassi, hech qanday dependency yo'q
class User {
  final String id;
  final String name;
  final String email;
  final DateTime createdAt;

  const User({
    required this.id,
    required this.name,
    required this.email,
    required this.createdAt,
  });
}

// domain/repositories/user_repository.dart
// Abstract interface — implementation haqida hech narsa bilmaydi
abstract class UserRepository {
  Future<Either<Failure, User>> getUser(String id);
  Future<Either<Failure, List<User>>> getAllUsers();
  Future<Either<Failure, Unit>> saveUser(User user);
  Future<Either<Failure, Unit>> deleteUser(String id);
}

// domain/usecases/get_user_usecase.dart
// Use Case — bitta ish bajaradi
class GetUserUseCase {
  final UserRepository repository;

  GetUserUseCase(this.repository);

  Future<Either<Failure, User>> call(String userId) {
    return repository.getUser(userId);
  }
}
```

## Data Layer

```dart
// data/models/user_model.dart
// Model — Entity'ning "data" versiyasi (JSON serialize/deserialize)
class UserModel extends User {
  const UserModel({
    required super.id,
    required super.name,
    required super.email,
    required super.createdAt,
  });

  factory UserModel.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) {
    return UserModel(
      id: json['id'],
      name: json['name'],
      email: json['email'],
      createdAt: DateTime.parse(json['created_at']),
    );
  }

  Map<String, dynamic> toJson() => {
    'id': id,
    'name': name,
    'email': email,
    'created_at': createdAt.toIso8601String(),
  };
}

// data/datasources/user_remote_datasource.dart
abstract class UserRemoteDataSource {
  Future<UserModel> getUser(String id);
}

class UserRemoteDataSourceImpl implements UserRemoteDataSource {
  final http.Client client;

  UserRemoteDataSourceImpl(this.client);

  @override
  Future<UserModel> getUser(String id) async {
    final response = await client.get(
      Uri.parse('https://api.example.com/users/$id'),
    );

    if (response.statusCode == 200) {
      return UserModel.fromJson(json.decode(response.body));
    } else {
      throw ServerException('Server xatosi: ${response.statusCode}');
    }
  }
}

// data/repositories/user_repository_impl.dart
class UserRepositoryImpl implements UserRepository {
  final UserRemoteDataSource remoteDataSource;
  final UserLocalDataSource localDataSource;
  final NetworkInfo networkInfo;

  UserRepositoryImpl({
    required this.remoteDataSource,
    required this.localDataSource,
    required this.networkInfo,
  });

  @override
  Future<Either<Failure, User>> getUser(String id) async {
    if (await networkInfo.isConnected) {
      try {
        final user = await remoteDataSource.getUser(id);
        await localDataSource.cacheUser(user); // Offline uchun saqlash
        return Right(user);
      } on ServerException catch (e) {
        return Left(ServerFailure(e.message));
      }
    } else {
      try {
        final user = await localDataSource.getCachedUser(id);
        return Right(user);
      } on CacheException {
        return Left(CacheFailure('Kesh topilmadi'));
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Presentation Layer — BLoC bilan

```dart
// presentation/bloc/user_bloc.dart
class UserBloc extends Bloc<UserEvent, UserState> {
  final GetUserUseCase getUserUseCase;

  UserBloc({required this.getUserUseCase}) : super(UserInitial()) {
    on<GetUserRequested>(_onGetUser);
  }

  Future<void> _onGetUser(
    GetUserRequested event,
    Emitter<UserState> emit,
  ) async {
    emit(UserLoading());

    final result = await getUserUseCase(event.userId);

    result.fold(
      (failure) => emit(UserError(failure.message)),
      (user) => emit(UserLoaded(user)),
    );
  }
}
```

## Dependency Injection — GetIt

```dart
// injection_container.dart
final sl = GetIt.instance;

Future<void> init() async {
  // BLoC
  sl.registerFactory(() => UserBloc(getUserUseCase: sl()));

  // Use Cases
  sl.registerLazySingleton(() => GetUserUseCase(sl()));

  // Repository
  sl.registerLazySingleton<UserRepository>(
    () => UserRepositoryImpl(
      remoteDataSource: sl(),
      localDataSource: sl(),
      networkInfo: sl(),
    ),
  );

  // Data sources
  sl.registerLazySingleton<UserRemoteDataSource>(
    () => UserRemoteDataSourceImpl(client: sl()),
  );

  // External
  sl.registerLazySingleton(() => http.Client());
}
```

Clean Architecture bilan yozilgan kod unit-test qilish uchun juda qulay chunki har bir qatlam mustaqil ravishda mock qilinishi mumkin.

